                                             Table "public.payments"
         Column          |           Type           | Collation | Nullable |               Default                
-------------------------+--------------------------+-----------+----------+--------------------------------------
 id                      | integer                  |           | not null | nextval('payments_id_seq'::regclass)
 user_id                 | integer                  |           | not null | 
 amount                  | numeric(14,2)            |           | not null | 
 click_merchant_trans_id | character varying(128)   |           | not null | 
 click_payment_id        | bigint                   |           |          | 
 status                  | character varying(32)    |           | not null | 'PENDING'::character varying
 created_at              | timestamp with time zone |           | not null | now()
 updated_at              | timestamp with time zone |           | not null | now()
Indexes:
    "payments_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "payments_click_merchant_trans_id_uq" UNIQUE, btree (click_merchant_trans_id)
    "payments_status_idx" btree (status)
    "payments_user_id_idx" btree (user_id)
Triggers:
    payments_set_updated_at BEFORE UPDATE ON payments FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION set_updated_at()

